{"tid":2024280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[批鬥] 黃嘅就唔應該收政府錢","createTime":"2020-05-19T13:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T13:58:25.000Z","uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a66b19184f36ff713046fc7007e6e9e6c3aa2263","tid":2024280,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:36:20.000Z","msg":"黃嘅唔攞d錢就去左紅藍度，點解唔收得？ <br />\n唔駛食？黃大仙？<br />\n無錢點支持黃色經濟圈？<br />\n<br />\n係，係有concern有youtuber收政府錢會幫政府漂白，不過你有一句係漂白就會露底，定係連登仔全部傻9驚自己睇唔穿？<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n收政府錢=撐政府 ❌<br />\n打政府工=撐政府 ❌<br />\n<br />\n另外得著<br />\n利益申報係值得鼓勵，減少好多疑慮，鼓勵每個youtuber都做，收左錢就認，要唔認有收錢果d唔好接。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚再批鬥啦</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">屎家軍係唔係黃都好，密切留意佢地帶風向行為</span>"},{"pid":"08035fc8a5a9a31fdab151435d47b1e72d002d6e","tid":2024280,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65532e23af19072b5b06bc7b6bc9c094f669c537","tid":2024280,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"收政府錢係應份，以前有份比，點解無份收？"},{"pid":"33898e3fe2ceb06cbe0675dee0573dff26a8841a","tid":2024280,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"啱 唔反牙gem了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b7bc6dbaf30330934e05cb09788277cd06d005","tid":2024280,"uid":267801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:51:11.000Z","msg":"請問政府啲錢邊度嚟！！！<br />\n攞返自己啲錢有咩問題！！"},{"pid":"0443b7ab91fa406bc13de50e5f446034073fa8f3","tid":2024280,"uid":65390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"收政府錢捐612"}]}